Hello! Thank you for calling Home Harmony Furniture. My name is Lisa. How can I assist you today?

Hi Lisa, I’m looking for a new dining table and wanted to get some information before visiting your store.

Absolutely, I’d be happy to help. May I have your name, please?

Sure, my name is Chris.

Thank you, Chris. What specific details are you looking for about our dining tables?

I’m interested in the materials used and if any of the tables are currently on sale.

We have a variety of tables made from solid wood and glass. Currently, we have a discount on some of our wooden tables. Can I get your email address to send you the latest catalog and promotions?

Sure, it’s chrisSmith at email dot com.

Great! I’ll send that right over. Could you also provide me with your phone number in case we have special offers in the future?

My phone number is five five five, one two three, four five six seven.

Thanks, Chris! I’ll ensure you receive all updates. Is there anything else I can assist you with?

No, that’s all for now. Thanks, Lisa!

You’re welcome, Chris! Thank you for calling Home Harmony Furniture. Have a great day!
